import React from "react";
import { AuthService } from "../../servieces/auth/authenticationServiece"; //Auth-api
import { AuthStore } from "../../mobx/auth-mobx/"; //mobx-auth-store



const authService = new AuthService(); //APIs
const authStore = new AuthStore(authService); // mobx-auth-store

export const StoreContext = React.createContext(); //mobx-auth-store
